node.text:
LEAVE A ❤️ IF THIS TOUCHED YOU DEEPLY

This story hits me so hard because as a child I too was doubted and criticized. 

I remember in the 3rd grade my teacher Miss Williams wanted to hold me back a grade. 

Deep down I knew I wasn’t “slow,” I just wasn’t interested or excited about the material. Fast forward many years and I wind up with a full academic scholarship to University, where I graduated with latin honors.

People may doubt you, they may criticize you. But don’t let them kill your dream, and definitely don’t let them kill your spirit!

@iamsteveharveytv

node.title: TEACHER HUMILIATES STUTTERING KID, GETS TAUGHT A LESSON

node.text:
LEAVE A 💯 IF YOU AGREE⁣ 
⁣
it is said that the majority of a child’s personality development takes place from age 0-7.⁣
⁣
This means that who that child will be for 80 years is determined by these first few years⁣
⁣
I believe it is the same for your day. The FIRST HOUR of your day determines the frequency you carry for the rest of the day.⁣
⁣
The only thing I would add to this list is making your bed and working out. Accomplishing tasks in the morning creates confidence and that confidence/momentum will carry over throughout the day⁣
⁣
 Much love ❤️

node.text:
Drop a ❤️ IF YOU TAKE CARE OF YOUR BODY.⁣
⁣
Since your skin (your largest organ) absorbs what you apply to it, my advice is try not to apply anything on your skin that you wouldn’t eat.⁣
⁣
This Johnson and Johnson debacle won’t be the first or last example of companies inserting harmful ingredients in a product.⁣
⁣
Read the labels, stick with single ingredient foods and products and you pretty much can’t go wrong.⁣
⁣
Take care of yourself ❤️⁣

node.text:
Drop a 🙏 if you practice YOGA.⁣
⁣
Asanas, or postures and poses are the first baby steps (limbs) in yogic practice. The fancy poses have nothing to do with an enlightened state, and often they can signify that one is trapped further in illusion (Maya)⁣
⁣
The ultimate goal of yoga is called samadhi...(no this isn’t a new IG filter). It means union with supreme consciousness.⁣
⁣
The funny part is...you’re already ONE with supreme consciousness and so yoga itself is an illusion used to wake you up to who you already are. In other words it’s a thorn to remove a thorn.⁣
⁣
❤️

It take a humble and intelligent person to acknowledge what they don’t know.⁣
⁣
The good news is...we can always stand on the shoulders of giants⁣
⁣
Whether it be books or mentors, there is ALWAYS a solution to EVERY PROBLEM. You simply have to LOOK. Often times the answer is closer than you thought
